queridometro.break_penalty: −0.15 × min(prev_streak, 15)/15 when positive streak ≥5 breaks negative

weights.decay: none — all events accumulate at full weight; queridômetro uses 3-day reactive window (70%) + streak memory (30%) + break penalty

context_notes.week_1: Pedro (most rejected, many planned to vote for him) quit on Jan 19, voting day. Participants redirected votes to Paulo Augusto despite weak animosity. Also first-week bonds were less established.
